preloadImages

public static void preloadImages(exCanvas forcan,
                                 java.lang.String Dir)
this is a fairly standard preloadImages method, called from the game initialization. It loads the images (all two of them) into a static array of hexChip which are used by all instances of the game.

Parameters:
forcan - the canvas for which we are loading the images.
Dir - the directory to find the image files.
